column9: b'Sporting a classic design, the 6-piece Royalford RF1097-GT6 Glass Tumbler Set is ideal for everyday use. Designed with a sturdy, tapering base, these tumblers are stable on various surfaces. They are also durable and long-lasting owing to the high-quality glass material. Built with a capacity of 230ml, this Royalford glass tumbler set lets you pour out an adequate amount of water or juice.'

column9: b"Crafted with a simple, classic design, the Royalford RF1101-GT6 Highball Glass Set is a must-have. Beautifully made from high-quality glass, this set is sturdy and durable. The tall design of this Royalford highball glass set makes it ideal for serving a range of cocktails or mixed drinks. What's more, thanks to its capacity of 325ml, this set of glasses lets you pour out the right quantity of drinks."
